Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇聖下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖下被…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 全員撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 不行 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.42,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:05.17,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽ばたいて行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:05.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飛出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:11.54,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界へ GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:11.54,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著嶄新的世界 GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手と手を繋いで進めば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要手牽手一起前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇さえ恐れず行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連黑暗也無足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:27.62,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰もまだ知らないあの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:27.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著未曾有人知曉的那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中で嵐に遭っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算途中遭遇暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:33.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見守る瞳の灯りが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:33.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你守望的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:38.12,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち向かう勇気をくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:38.12,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予了我奮勇抗爭的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:44.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法より強い力さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:44.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是比魔法更強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:50.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かけがえのない君を思う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:50.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心懷無可替代的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:55.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この場 ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:55.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立於此地 ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:01.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:01.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你我之間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:06.78,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しさも唇も強気な眼差しも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:06.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的寂寞 你的嘴唇 你的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きさ ALWAYS I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都喜歡喔  ALWAYS I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らなら出来る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的話一定可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:17.81,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷ついて 乗り越えて 心から笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:17.81,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路受傷一路克服 發自真心的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:24.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界へ GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:24.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著嶄新的世界 GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德魯弗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德魯弗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律特斯的貝爾薩爾提宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律特斯的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 遠古巨龍呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨龍怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止活動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就在快要穿過奧魯奇亞溪谷的時候 突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大塊頭就像岩石一樣蜷成一團不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為教皇聖下的力量導致巨龍死亡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是能持續聽到巨龍的脈搏聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與心跳相呼應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久後就會醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不僅於此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯曼院長 您也來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇聖下的事真的很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在的當務之急是要把遠古巨龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖下也一定是如此期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 叫老夫前來應該就是為了那遠古巨龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 奧斯曼院長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一邊擔任魔法學園的院長 一邊進行研究的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那傢伙還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次我們一定要打敗牠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給教皇報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 露易絲 蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪絲塔 有什麼吃的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我馬上去把湯熱一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 學院的大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都回托里斯汀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露可夏娜小姐他們說是要一起去才人先生的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以倒是留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 但是估計還要過一段時間才能回宅邸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫雪絲塔的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不…下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人沒說一句有關德魯弗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他明明非常悲傷的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…因為才人先生他很堅強啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定在竭盡全力的忍耐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不堅強也沒有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他索性就說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沒有德魯弗就不能戰鬥了」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不會再使用里維斯拉謝爾的力量了」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在責怪蒂法妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再看到才人繼續削減自己的生命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望才人死去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於遠古巨龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫翻閱文獻得到的結論就是以上這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 對於露易絲和蒂法妮婭來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待她們的是前所未有的殘酷試煉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 關於這件事 之後老夫打算親自告訴她們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「四之四」沒有齊聚的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣對抗巨龍是不是個錯誤啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 根據傳說所言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去打倒巨龍的是「四之四」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 並沒有說除了他們之外 其他人就什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在這六千年裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的文明也急速發展
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的哈爾凱尼亞 還存在著超越國界的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也許就能填補尚且欠缺的「四之四」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特女王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托里斯汀會全軍出動對抗此次災厄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知高盧可否與我們一起並肩作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去請求羅馬尼亞和其他各國的協助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾凱尼亞的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們自己的雙手來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對抗巨龍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以組建了哈爾凱尼亞全土的聯軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 由我來指揮全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 遠古巨龍不靠我們這些「虛無繼承者」的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 我們所有人都是出生於哈爾凱尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由哈爾凱尼亞養育長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以面對這種世界危機我們無法袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算機會渺茫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會為打倒巨龍的可能性而放手一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也打算一起奔赴戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 只要還有一口氣在就會繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為出生於哈爾凱尼亞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向這個世界獻出我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起克服這次危機吧 絕對可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為出生於哈爾凱尼亞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向這個世界獻出我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是哈爾凱尼亞人 所以這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是才人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人並不是在這個世界出生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他牽扯進來真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快做好出征的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去打倒巨龍了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別落隊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得幹啊 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是傷感的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？德魯弗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？沉沒在我綠洲裡的機器？是指那個鐵筒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算利用那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那東西已經壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在妖精的國度裡 有沒有別的那種東西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被慎重的保管在某處之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 沒聽說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為搞不好有可能呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有戰鬥機的話 遠古巨龍什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就能打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西是叫做戰鬥機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我那個世界的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在空中高速飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 用導彈的話連軍艦都能擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這麼厲害的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先回一趟你的國家 再把它拿過來不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個的話稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼使用露易絲的魔法如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是指世界之門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事能辦得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦不到的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我的世界啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著用世界之門連接才人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果順利的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 我們一起去拿那個戰鬥機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 幹吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 確認一下步驟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先露易絲向才人的國家打開一扇窗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs30}再利用才人的力量把窗戶擴大到可以讓人通過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是他在指揮啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs30}然後才人跟露易絲兩人一起前往才人的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜歡這樣啦 就睜一隻眼閉一隻眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到戰鬥機後再次利用露易絲的魔法回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能回到我的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油喔 才人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多該開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我稍微借用一下才人的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你那個世界的印象傳送給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}（咒語）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 通往才人世界的大門啊 打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的建築
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是才人先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 是我的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 才人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與你相遇 真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 請你記得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後我展現給你的表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笑容喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 妳做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露…露易絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦利埃爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹了什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打敗巨龍 他是不可或缺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人他…是從別的世界過來的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要讓他承擔這個世界的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕他是虛無的使魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦利埃爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 才人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲小姐是真心愛著才人先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話 是不會做出這種選擇的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我把他送回原本的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉 但是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定會做同樣的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔帕莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 肯定這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不借助里維斯拉謝爾的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會靠我自身的力量打倒巨龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會賭上自己的一切 加入戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去魔法學院啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實好像過去封印了遠古巨龍的是虛無的繼承者們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從文獻來看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎繼承者們也同時給予了遠古巨龍力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過被巨龍吞食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨龍透過吞食虛無而變得強大起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此那傢伙會憑藉本能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著虛無繼承者的所在地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 巨龍一開始前往羅馬利亞是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為感受到了虛無繼承人之一的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇聖下他的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 等到那傢伙醒來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來盯上的人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或者是蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才把妳們帶回魔法學院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的話 周圍沒有什麼集落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需擔心民眾被牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對已經預料到的巨龍行進路線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊也準備好了盡可能的利用炮擊拖住巨龍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道能起多大的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該能爭取一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是在魔法學院戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學院裡的人該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯爾貝爾老師已經指揮大家去避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪絲塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了要妳和露可夏娜他們去宅邸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜託她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很想見識一下魔法學院嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裡很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都去避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 露易絲 蒂法妮婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家正在商量我想出的 為了打敗巨龍的陣型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 妳們兩個快過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔帕莎小姐 妳剛才不是還在王宮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用最快速度飛過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趕超過你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 奧斯曼院長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不聽我的話 都留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我早就料到會這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡的話也許會死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼可能置身事外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也想保護自己生活的這個世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們「水精靈騎士隊」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有代替才人保護妳們的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這種事 不覺得有些刺激嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑奈特 為什麼你們會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我僱用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是傭兵 認錢不認人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為同伴來說 我們還是蠻可靠的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我們 也不希望世界毀滅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能多一個先住魔法的使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能省去很多功夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 露可夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不過如果能在這裡阻止巨龍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了涅夫提斯好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 要吃夜宵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我在那個時候露出了那種窩囊的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我繼續使用里維斯拉謝爾的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲才會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果沒有這個力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法打倒遠古巨龍的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…露易絲會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 這裡打開了一扇光之門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就被召喚過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被喜歡的女僕給甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 難不成你在哭鼻子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這熊樣肯定要被甩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了閉上你們的狗嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我們費了這麼多勁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果這傢伙身上一分錢都沒有 白費勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我一個人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法回到哈爾凱尼亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…再也見不到面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在成長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等巨大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥快退下 退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正前方有什麼東西正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說從正面而來？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠古巨龍！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說那傢伙還能飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上進行攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:07.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,めちゃめちゃ 大好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:07.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級無敵喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもでも ムカツク
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是好生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:12.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kissして おねがい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:12.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了給我一個吻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:15.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kissして あげない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:15.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不給你甜吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:20.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハラハラ イライラその態度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:20.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人擔心不已 焦躁不已的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別にヤキモチじゃないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是在吃醋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:25.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ホラホラ チラチラ誰見てるの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:25.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我說 你到底在偷看誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.69,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ありえないでしょ!?それって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事完全不可能吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:30.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゼロからあなたをしつけなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:30.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得從零開始好好調教你才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.86,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍛え直してあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你脫胎換骨的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:37.32,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひざまずいたらワン!と鳴きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:37.32,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪下後大喊一聲汪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:38.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早くおすわりっ!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:38.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:44.38,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙女ゴコロは微妙(だってビンカンよ)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:44.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女心思好微妙（因為好敏感）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:48.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当は胸がいっぱいなの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:48.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你早已填滿了我的胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:50.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あんたはドンカンっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:50.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太遲鈍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全密着 そばにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親密無間 待在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:55.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断然 私を愛して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:55.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅然 愛著我直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋する女の子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為戀愛中的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:01.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱりよくばりなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:01.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然都是貪心鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:04.61,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間接着 抱きよせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:04.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間接近 緊緊抱著我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:06.92,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,単純 つまりは一途に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:06.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純 也就是一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:10.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あきれるくらいにね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:10.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用多到讓我覺得厭煩的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:12.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私だけに恋をして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:12.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅愛著我一個人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:15.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,めちゃめちゃ 大好き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:15.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級無敵喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:18.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもでも ムカツク
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:18.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是好生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:20.87,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kissして おねがい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:20.87,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了給我一個吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:24.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kissして あげないケド
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:24.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我才不會給你甜吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.87,0:23:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你一定在屬於你的世界裡生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一點都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 最終話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零之使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 一直以來謝謝你了
